ZH: 这个问题对我来说微不足道。
EN: This problem is trivial to me.

ZH: 她只是犯了一个微不足道的错误。
EN: She just made a trivial mistake.

ZH: 这个鸟窝对于大象来说微不足道。
EN: This bird's nest is trivial for an elephant.

ZH: 对他来说，这次失败微不足道。
EN: This failure is trivial for him.

ZH: 即使有些小错误，我们也可以说微不足道。
EN: Even with some small mistakes, we can say it is trivial.

ZH: 你的年龄微不足道，不应该放弃梦想。
EN: Your age is trivial, you should not give up your dreams.

ZH: 谢谢你的帮助，虽然微不足道但我很感激。
EN: Thank you for your help, it may be trivial, but I am very grateful.

ZH: 这笔钱对于富人来说是微不足道的。
EN: This amount of money is trivial for rich people.

ZH: 对于一位专业音乐家来说，这个曲子微不足道。
EN: This piece is trivial for a professional musician.

ZH: 他把朋友和家人的意见看作是微不足道的。
EN: He considers the opinions of friends and family to be trivial.

ZH: 即使是一点微不足道的帮助，我也会感激不尽。
EN: Even a trivial help would be greatly appreciated.

ZH: 年龄的差别对于他们的友谊是微不足道的。
EN: The age difference is trivial to their friendship.

ZH: 你不必为这些问题的微不足道而担心。
EN: You don't have to worry about the triviality of these problems.

ZH: 他总是试图夸大微不足道的问题。
EN: He always tries to exaggerate trivial issues.

ZH: 对于大公司来说，这是一个微不足道的投资。
EN: This is a trivial investment for a big company.

ZH: 请原谅我给你带来的微不足道的麻烦。
EN: Please forgive me for the trivial trouble I caused you.

ZH: 我不能仅仅因为微不足道的挫折而放弃努力。
EN: I can't give up my efforts just because of trivial setbacks.

ZH: 不要将一些微不足道的事情变成大问题。
EN: Don't turn trivial matters into big issues.

ZH: 他对微不足道的细节非常挑剔。
EN: He is very picky about trivial details.

ZH: 我们不应该在这些微不足道的事情上花费太多时间。
EN: We shouldn't spend too much time on these trivial matters.
